Class Order

  • java.lang.Object
    • Event
      • Order

  • public class Order
extends Event
    This entity class is a subclass of the Event entity class, and stores all information relevant to a order such as DateTime, Customer Name, Pax, Table and Staff. In particular, it stores two arrays of items and packages respectively that is managed by the OrderManager class.
